titles.title: Dismissing the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the First Congressional District of Hawaii.

action.text: The House Committee on House Administration reported an original measure, H. Rept. 111-68, by Mr. Brady (PA).

calendar.text: Placed on the House Calendar, Calendar No. 36.

action.text: Mr. Brady (PA) filed a privileged report from the Committee on House Administration on H. Res. 303.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to by voice vote.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 3/31/2009--Passed House without amendment. Dismisses the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the 1st congressional district of Hawaii.
